    <item>
      <title>银行出售 10 亿美元贷款以资助收购 Jaggaer</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/banks-sell-1-billion-of-loans-to-fund-buyout-of-jaggaer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以瑞银集团为首的银行出售了 10 亿美元的杠杆贷款，以帮助 Vista Equity Partners 收购软件公司 Jaggaer，这是市场上最新的包含第二留置权部分的收购交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/banks-sell-1-billion-of-loans-to-fund-buyout-of-jaggaer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ares 的 deVeer 认为美联储降息将催化未来交易流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ares-deveer-sees-fed-rate-cuts-catalyzing-future-deal-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ares Management Corp. 信贷部门主管 Kipp deVeer 表示，尽管美联储降息可能会削弱所有浮动利率信贷的回报，但宽松周期仍将成为交易的催化剂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ares-deveer-sees-fed-rate-cuts-catalyzing-future-deal-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风米尔顿逼近佛罗里达，保险公司对海伦飓风的损失估计上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/insurers-helene-loss-estimates-climb-as-they-brace-for-milton</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管保险公司正在为飓风米尔顿可能造成的更大破坏做准备，但飓风海伦造成的保险损失估计已攀升至 140 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/insurers-helene-loss-estimates-climb-as-they-brace-for-milton</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗仍在从哈格岛主要码头运输原油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/iran-is-still-shipping-crude-oil-from-key-kharg-island-terminal-satellite-photo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管大批油轮已逃离附近海域（它们通常会在附近海域等待收集货物），伊朗仍在从其主要哈格岛码头出口原油。]]></description>
