      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购“悬念”令穆巴达拉炼油厂债券持有人感到不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/takeover-suspense-unnerves-mubadala-s-refinery-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆巴达拉资本 (Mubadala Capital) 旗下的炼油厂运营商 Acelen 的投资者正在失去耐心，因为与巴西国有石油公司 Petroleo Brasileiro SA 的潜在出售谈判持续拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/takeover-suspense-unnerves-mubadala-s-refinery-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vista 的 Alegeus 在摆脱私人信贷方面遭遇障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/vista-s-alegeus-hits-roadblock-in-effort-to-shed-private-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alegeus Technologies 在私人信贷债务再融资方面遭遇了延迟，这对于历史上繁忙的美国杠杆贷款市场来说是一次罕见的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/vista-s-alegeus-hits-roadblock-in-effort-to-shed-private-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
